Maybe not completely.

428
0:19:53.96 --> 0:19:57.70
我以为自己弄丢了  原来是你偷了
I thought I lost this and it turns out it was stolen.

429
0:20:00.34 --> 0:20:02.00
抱歉  医生
I'm sorry Doctor

430
0:20:03.15 --> 0:20:05.88
但是我们一定要保持联系
But it's important we be in contact.

431
0:20:08.57 --> 0:20:10.59
我们有点
We're in the middle of a...

432
0:20:12.42 --> 0:20:13.72
争执
disagreement.

433
0:20:13.74 --> 0:20:15.72
你和那个声音有争执
A disagreement with the voice?

434
0:20:20.38 --> 0:20:23.09
我希望你知道  我无条件支持你
I want you to know that I support you unconditionally.

435
0:20:26.24 --> 0:20:28.08
我理解你认为自己需要电话
Now I know you believe you need a phone

436
0:20:28.18 --> 0:20:30.23
但我还是要说  你不需要
And I'm here to tell you that you don't.

437
0:20:30.23 --> 0:20:32.46
我相信禁止你碰它
I believe that by separating you from it--

438
0:20:32.46 --> 0:20:34.87
以及其他所有科技产品
and from all other forms of technology--

439
0:20:34.88 --> 0:20:36.75
是目前的最佳方法
It's really the best course of action.

440
0:20:36.75 --> 0:20:38.53
拒绝科技吧
So it's time to unplug.

441
0:20:39.30 --> 0:20:40.76
请几位助手进来
Some assistance please.

442
0:20:41.19 --> 0:20:44.89
拜托  别这样
Please... don't do this.

443
0:20:45.66 --> 0:20:47.95
不能把我们分开
It's not good for us to be separated.

444
0:20:48.30 --> 0:20:50.28
希望你明白  我是在帮你
I hope you realize I'm trying to help you.

445
0:20:52.21 --> 0:20:54.75
把这位病人送到隔离病房
Escort our patient to solitary confinement.

446
0:20:54.76 --> 0:20:57.12
不得接触任何电子设备
No contact with anything electronic.

447
0:20:57.53 --> 0:20:58.93
有朝一日你会感谢我
You'll thank me someday.

448
0:20:59.31 --> 0:21:01.17
身为心理医生
For a psychiatrist

449
0:21:02.59 --> 0:21:05.39
你真是太不会看人了
you're really a terrible judge of character.

450
0:21:12.17 --> 0:21:13.35
我们来这干什么
What are we doing here?

451
0:21:13.76 --> 0:21:14.64
侦察
Recon.

452
0:21:15.12 --> 0:21:17.18
十点在那儿交易
The exchange goes down there in ten.

453
0:21:18.34 --> 0:21:21.33
那里  特种部队肯定安排有狙击手
That's it. Spec ops will have a sniper.

454
0:21:22.06 --> 0:21:23.33
要我就会在那里
That's where I'd be.

455
0:21:23.85 --> 0:21:25.10
有零钱吗
You got any cash?

456
0:21:32.56 --> 0:21:33.47
你好啊
Hola mija.

457
0:21:33.47 --> 0:21:35.23
真不知道我怎么会落到这步田地
Don't know how I wound up here.

458
0:21:35.58 --> 0:21:36.52
我知道
I do.

459
0:21:37.18 --> 0:21:39.99
和你跟锅盖头打架是一个原因
Same reason you got into a fight with those jarheads.

460
0:21:42.51 --> 0:21:44.61
你为自己在乎的人挺身而出
You stand up for people you care about.

461
0:21:45.37 --> 0:21:46.93
我是大受其益啊
Lotta good it's done me huh?

462
0:21:47.34 --> 0:21:48.37
等着瞧吧
We'll see.

463
0:21:48.89 --> 0:21:50.67
本性难移
You can't be something you're not.

464
0:21:51.09 --> 0:21:54.22
是吗  那我的本性是什么
Yeah? And who am I?

465
0:21:55.45 --> 0:21:57.09
你是好人  杰克
You're a good guy Jack.

466
0:21:58.35 --> 0:22:00.49
只是你自己还没明白
You just haven't figured it out yet.

467
0:22:02.94 --> 0:22:03.97
谢谢
Gracias.

468
0:22:09.05 --> 0:22:11.30
干嘛  要帮忙找垃圾桶吗
What you need help finding a trash can?

469
0:22:12.37 --> 0:22:14.82
你聪明啊  自己想该怎么用
You're a smart guy you'll figure out what to do with it.

470
0:22:15.76 --> 0:22:17.08
给我三分钟
Give me three minutes.

471
0:22:43.24 --> 0:22:45.16
陆战队的武器妙啊
Our leatherneck has a nice weapon.

472
0:22:45.26 --> 0:22:46.70
这下就好玩了
This is gonna be fun.

473
0:22:46.78 --> 0:22:48.05
记住
Just remember...

474
0:22:49.36 --> 0:22:50.89
不许射要害
no shots to center mass.

475
0:22:50.89 --> 0:22:53.95
这么好的枪拿来打膝盖可惜了
But it's a shame to waste a rifle like this on kneecaps.

476
0:22:56.90 --> 0:22:58.73
没岗哨  不对劲
No sentry. Something's up.

477
0:22:58.77 --> 0:23:02.10
能看到房间里吗  有谁
You got eyes on the room? Who's there?

478
0:23:02.10 --> 0:23:03.29
空荡荡
Looks vacated.

479
0:23:03.75 --> 0:23:06.08
情有可原  那可怜人被装上炸弹了
For good reason poor guy's rigged up to go boom.

480
0:23:10.62 --> 0:23:11.53
别
Don't.

481
0:23:11.95 --> 0:23:13.61
别引爆了
Can't risk setting him off.

482
0:23:17.87 --> 0:23:19.99
你朋友坐在简易炸弹上
Your friend's sitting on an IED.

483
0:23:28.99 --> 0:23:31.68
抱歉把你卷进来  杰克
Look I'm sorry I got you into this Jack

484
0:23:32.71 --> 0:23:35.19
但你要是能把我弄出去
But if you can get me outta here

485
0:23:35.19 --> 0:23:37.47
我发誓会承担一切责任
I swear I'll rap to everything.

486
0:23:37.87 --> 0:23:41.29
放松  你没事的
Take it easy. You're gonna be okay.

487
0:23:42.36 --> 0:23:43.62
那可不一定
I wouldn't say that.

488
0:23:44.92 --> 0:23:48.69
我们说过要一个人来  你却带上了这西装男
We told you to come alone. You brought the suit

489
0:23:49.01 --> 0:23:51.11
那他也要跟着倒霉了
So now he's a guest at our party.

490
0:23:51.22 --> 0:23:55.24
他要走  我们就按按钮  RJ爆炸
He tries to leave we hit a button RJ explodes.

491
0:23:55.24 --> 0:23:58.15
你敢动RJ  他爆炸
You try to move RJ he explodes.

492
0:23:58.15 --> 0:24:00.00
明白了吗  水兵
You understand me squid?

493
0:24:00.00 --> 0:24:01.26
知道了
I get the gist.

494
0:24:01.26 --> 0:24:02.69
毁掉手机
Destroy your phone.

495
0:24:10.00 --> 0:24:13.30
路边有辆出租车  载你去下一站
There's a cab on the curb that'll take you to the next location

496
0:24:13.30 --> 0:24:14.12
一个人
alone.

497
0:24:17.51 --> 0:24:19.42
你出了那门  杰克
You walk out that door Jack

498
0:24:20.58 --> 0:24:21.89
可能就回不来了
you won't come back.

499
0:24:25.95 --> 0:24:27.32
RJ是我的朋友
RJ's my friend.

500
0:24:28.34 --> 0:24:29.67
你也说过
You said it yourself.

501
0:24:31.51 --> 0:24:33.22
本性难移
I can't be something I'm not.

502
0:24:55.85 --> 0:24:58.32
哈罗德  交易有变
Harold the exchange went pear-shaped.

503
0:24:58.32 --> 0:25:01.08
我听到了  你能跟踪萨拉查先生吗
Yes I heard. Can you follow Mr. Salazar?

504
0:25:01.08 --> 0:25:02.87
不行  他已经走远了
Not an option. He's long gone.

505
0:25:02.87 --> 0:25:05.08
还没试试这小可爱呢
Never even got to take this baby out for a test drive.

506
0:25:05.08 --> 0:25:07.96
那些未切割钻石  陆战队员肯定得销赃
The marines will have to fence the uncut diamonds.

507
0:25:07.97 --> 0:25:10.27
找到销赃的  我们应该就能找到杰克
Locate the fence odds are we can locate Jack.

508
0:25:10.27 --> 0:25:11.16
现在去哪儿
Where to now?

509
0:25:11.16 --> 0:25:12.77
我另有人手在追查此事
I have another resource working on that.

510
0:25:12.77 --> 0:25:14.14
你自便
Suit yourself.

511
0:25:18.42 --> 0:25:20.87
抢劫组那边有消息吗
Any luck with your contacts in robbery?

512
0:25:20.87 --> 0:25:25.04
还没有  别担心  我有路子
Not yet. Don't worry I got a source.

514
0:25:36.98 --> 0:25:39.21
不是说表现良好可以放假么
What happened to time off for good behavior?

515
0:25:39.21 --> 0:25:41.14
前提是你表现良好
That assumes you've been good.

516
0:25:41.49 --> 0:25:44.34
我们有约定  你要保持低调
We had a deal you keep a low profile.

517
0:25:45.00 --> 0:25:47.85
否则我何必在地下室享受巴罗洛呢
Why else would I be enjoying my Barolo in a basement?

518
0:25:47.85 --> 0:25:50.37
你的人在皇冠高地出现了
Your man's been seen in Crown Heights

519
0:25:50.37 --> 0:25:52.03
那是俄罗斯人的地盘
Russian territory.

520
0:25:52.73 --> 0:25:54.58
现在全城都是俄罗斯人的地盘了
It's all Russian territory now.

521
0:25:56.47 --> 0:25:58.15
让我们单独聊下
Give us a moment alone.

522
0:26:05.60 --> 0:26:09.14
谢谢你  救了我老大
Thank you... for helping my boss.

523
0:26:12.40 --> 0:26:14.05
看看你  都交上朋友了
What do you know you've made a friend.

524
0:26:15.30 --> 0:26:16.83
说到朋友  我不禁注意到
Speaking of I can't help but notice

525
0:26:16.83 --> 0:26:19.81
哈罗德和约翰都没来看望过我
that I haven't received a visit from Harold or John.

526
0:26:20.19 --> 0:26:21.83
你还没有告诉他们  是吧
Haven't told them yet have you?

527
0:26:22.22 --> 0:26:24.04
怕他们反对我们的小约定吗
Afraid they'd object to our little deal?

528
0:26:24.04 --> 0:26:27.27
没有约定  我是别无选择
There's no deal okay I had no choice.

529
0:26:27.28 --> 0:26:28.54
如果我把你重新关进监狱  
If I'd put you back in prison

530
0:26:28.69 --> 0:26:31.10
就会有人  警察或是俄罗斯人
someone--cops or the Russians--

531
0:26:31.10 --> 0:26:33.24
迟早都会杀了你
would've killed you sooner or later.

532
0:26:35.27 --> 0:26:36.48
我要一个名字
I need a name

533
0:26:37.69 --> 0:26:41.94
有办法销赃大批未切割钻石的人
someone with the means to fence large quantities of uncut diamonds.

534
0:26:43.66 --> 0:26:45.60
如果有人想要做这样的交易
If someone is interested in such a transaction

535
0:26:45.60 --> 0:26:48.08
他们必须要联系个快速销赃人
They'd have to connect with a mobile fence

536
0:26:48.08 --> 0:26:50.81
有个不择手段的俄罗斯人
and I can think of an unscrupulous Russian

537
0:26:50.81 --> 0:26:52.74
名字叫马克西姆
by the name of Maksim

538
0:26:53.66 --> 0:26:57.45
他在熨斗区经营一间当铺
presently operating out of a pawn shop in the Flatiron District.

539
0:27:00.56 --> 0:27:03.69
小心  这很危险  警探
Careful this is dangerous business Detective.

540
0:27:06.24 --> 0:27:07.87
现在是警员了
It's officer now.

541
0:27:07.95 --> 0:27:11.01
多可惜啊  我最恨暴殄天物
Such a shame I hate seeing talent go to waste.

542
0:27:11.01 --> 0:27:13.20
我可以搞垮HR和俄罗斯人  
I could take care of HR and the Russians...

543
0:27:13.69 --> 0:27:14.90
永远地
permanently.

544
0:27:18.23 --> 0:27:20.28
享受你的巴罗洛吧
Enjoy the rest of your Barolo.

545
0:27:28.76 --> 0:27:30.24
情况如何  芬奇
How's it going Finch?

546
0:27:30.24 --> 0:27:32.71
我拦截了手机信号塔的信号
I've intercepted the signal at the cell tower.

547
0:27:33.24 --> 0:27:34.81
制作了一个循环影像
I'm creating a loop to send

548
0:27:34.81 --> 0:27:37.20
发送给他们的头目
back down the line to the team leader.

549
0:27:37.20 --> 0:27:39.46
他看不到你离开房间
It'll appear to him as if you never left the room.

550
0:27:41.46 --> 0:27:43.14
完成  你可以离开了  里瑟先生
All done. You can leave Mr. Reese.

551
0:27:43.14 --> 0:27:46.31
我建议你快点走  我派了增援
I suggest you do so in a hurry. I've sent reinforcements.

552
0:27:46.31 --> 0:27:47.32
谁
Who?

553
0:27:54.45 --> 0:27:56.22
你们真是一刻不消停
Never a dull moment with you guys.

554
0:27:58.20 --> 0:28:00.01
给  卡特给的
Here Carter came through.

555
0:28:00.49 --> 0:28:02.75
是熨斗区的一处销赃地址
Address for the fence in the Flatiron District.

556
0:28:04.03 --> 0:28:05.01
你准备好了吗
You ready?

557
0:28:05.65 --> 0:28:07.90
那些老毛子凶狠残忍  火力强大
These ruskies are ruthless and packin' serious heat.

558
0:28:07.90 --> 0:28:09.50
这活儿适合肖
Sounds like a job for Shaw.

559
0:28:09.50 --> 0:28:11.88
还有  这位身上的炸弹得拆
Besides someone needs to defuse that bomb.

560
0:28:12.10 --> 0:28:13.26
加油  莱奈尔
Hup to Lionel.

561
0:28:13.26 --> 0:28:15.56
什么  没人跟我说要拆炸弹
What? Nobody said anything about defusing a bomb.

562
0:28:15.56 --> 0:28:18.01
小心点  有断电保护
Be careful it's got a fail safe.

563
0:28:18.01 --> 0:28:19.82
如果切断电源  就会爆炸
If you try to cut the power source it'll blow

564
0:28:19.82 --> 0:28:21.41
所以要拆掉点火装置
So dig out the igniter.

565
0:28:22.08 --> 0:28:23.02
啥装置
The what?

566
0:28:49.79 --> 0:28:52.62
你的石子儿我带来了  你不敢出来玩了吗
I got your rocks. You afraid to come out and play?

567
0:28:53.02 --> 0:28:56.77
你还以为是你说了算吗  水手小子
You still think you're in charge of this little operation swab-jockey?

568
0:28:56.77 --> 0:28:58.72
不好说  反正我捏着你的货
Don't know. I got your whole stash.

569
0:28:58.72 --> 0:29:02.77
好啊  我捏着小小的保险  你的兄弟RJ
Yeah well I got a little insurance policy your buddy RJ.

570
0:29:03.32 --> 0:29:05.93
23大街和莱辛顿大道的十字路口有家当铺
There's a pawn shop at 23rd and Lex.

571
0:29:06.23 --> 0:29:07.18
那又怎么了
What about it?

572
0:29:07.18 --> 0:29:09.91
你跟销赃人玩个"谈交易"的游戏
You're gonna play "Let's make a deal" with our fence.

573
0:29:10.08 --> 0:29:13.38
你把钻石给他  然后换来现金带给我们
You bring him the diamonds and you bring us the cash.

574
0:29:13.38 --> 0:29:16.64
你要是耍什么花招  就等着被收尸吧
You tries to pull a fast one you end up in a body bag.

575
0:29:16.94 --> 0:29:19.90
时间不等人  海军士官
Time's ticking petty officer.

576
0:29:36.96 --> 0:29:38.41
陆战魔要过多久会发现
How long before the devil dog realizes

577
0:29:38.41 --> 0:29:40.01
你朋友篡改了影像
your friend switched the video?

578
0:29:40.82 --> 0:29:43.92
很久  但愿吧
Long enough... let's hope.

579
0:29:44.14 --> 0:29:45.96
你是海军  知道点火装置在哪儿吗
You're in the navy. Know anything about igniters?

580
0:29:45.97 --> 0:29:47.49
伙计  我是个"光荣"的仓管员
Man I'm a glorified shopkeeper.

581
0:29:47.60 --> 0:29:49.47
只管补给品
I inventory supplies.

582
0:29:49.85 --> 0:29:51.35
别担心  我是警察
Don't worry I'm a cop.

583
0:29:52.57 --> 0:29:53.64
拆弹组的
Bomb squad?

584
0:29:53.64 --> 0:29:54.64
凶案组的
Homicide.

586
0:30:08.50 --> 0:30:09.97
有东西要给我吗
You have something for me?

587
0:30:24.09 --> 0:30:26.56
你不是跟我通电话的人
You're not the one who I talked to on the phone.

588
0:30:28.42 --> 0:30:29.64
是游客吗
You're a tourist?

589
0:30:31.19 --> 0:30:32.47
可以这么说
Guess you could say that.

590
0:30:34.60 --> 0:30:38.15
那你只能拿到游客价  面值的30%
Then you get the tourist rate. 30 cents on the dollar.

591
0:30:38.32 --> 0:30:41.63
等等  你不明白你搞的是什么人
Wait you don't understand who you're screwing with.

592
0:30:41.95 --> 0:30:45.35
什么人  没枪没支援的人
Who? A man with no gun and no backup?

593
0:30:45.77 --> 0:30:48.90
也许我们会留下钱和钻石
Maybe we keep our money and your diamonds.

594
0:30:51.26 --> 0:30:53.39
我们不二价
We don't renegotiate.

595
0:30:59.74 --> 0:31:01.72
天天刀口舔血
Another fine navy day.

596
0:31:03.17 --> 0:31:04.77
你一定是马克西姆吧
You must be Maksim.

597
0:31:06.89 --> 0:31:10.43
你说过是面值的50%
You said 50 cents on the dollar.

598
0:31:10.43 --> 0:31:13.07
那是在我看到货之前
That was before I saw the merchandise.

599
0:31:13.37 --> 0:31:15.76
你之前没说是非洲货
You failed to mention it's from Africa.

600
0:31:15.93 --> 0:31:18.07
你不走运  我读了报道
Unfortunately for you I have read all about

601
0:31:18.07 --> 0:31:21.40
知道海盗被陆战队拿下的事
the pirates and the marine heroes who took them down.

602
0:31:24.07 --> 0:31:25.92
来见你  风险很大
Took big risk coming meeting you.

603
0:31:29.80 --> 0:31:31.92
风险越大  价格越低
Risk goes up price goes down.

604
0:31:35.76 --> 0:31:37.46
我给一百二
I give you 1.2.

605
0:31:41.27 --> 0:31:44.14
你觉得要给我多少我才不会干掉你
How much for me to not put a bullet in your brain?

606
0:31:44.34 --> 0:31:46.03
把枪放下
Put your weapon down!

607
0:32:03.64 --> 0:32:06.15
不好意思  你们打烊了吗
I'm sorry are you guys closed?

609
0:32:16.90 --> 0:32:18.69
气氛有点紧张
It's a bit tense in here.

610
0:32:23.32 --> 0:32:25.04
我提个建议如何
Can I make a suggestion?

611
0:32:25.26 --> 0:32:26.62
你在这里干什么
What the hell are you doing here?

